      "role": "user",
      "content": "right, segregate them. that's a good point. but it's honestly been so strange. the security footage just shows these weird gaps or little blurs where items used to be sitting, and the sensors don't even trip. it's almost like they're being taken by something small that knows exactly how to avoid the cameras. how do we even begin to investigate something that feels that... unconventional?",
